          <h1>Do you want to see some badges?</h1>
          <p>Too bad. This is it. Use your imagination?</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="http://backpack.openbadges.org/share/9d297b7173ab24665a1fe47e5111d1ab/" role="button">Retreat!</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAGZmZgAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="Second slide">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Meow</h1>
          <blockquote>"I love this badge with the space cat on it! It gives me a real sense of achievement"</blockquote>
          <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="http://backpack.openbadges.org/share/9d297b7173ab24665a1fe47e5111d1ab/" role="button">Space Adventure!</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAFVVVQAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="Third slide">
